            "notes": "The deck aims to quickly cycle through cards and fill the graveyard with powerful creatures like Colossal Skyturtle, Curator of Mysteries, and Endurance. Once the graveyard is stocked, the player can cast Living End to bring all those creatures back onto the battlefield, overwhelming the opponent with a sudden surge of powerful threats. Using cards like Violent Outburst and Subtlety to cascade into Living End can catch opponents off guard, while cards like Force of Negation provide protection against disruption. The key concept is to set up and execute a game-winning combo using graveyard recursion."
